<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Real Estate Landing</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
  <!-- Bootstrap CSS CDN -->
<link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    html, body {
      height: 100%;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background-color: #0d1117;
      color: white;
    }

    .page-wrapper {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px 40px;
      background-color: #0d1117;
    }

    .title {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #58a6ff;
      font-family: Georgia, 'Times New Roman', Times, serif;
      white-space: nowrap;
    }

    .auth-buttons {
      display: flex;
      gap: 15px;
    }

    .button {
      background-color: #238636;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 8px 18px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-weight: bold;
      transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
    }

    .button:hover {
      background-color: #2ea043;
    }

    .main-content {
      flex: 1;
      padding: 40px 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 32px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    h2 {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 26px;
      margin-top: 60px;
      color: #58a6ff;
    }

    .property-list {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 20px;
      margin: 30px auto;
      padding: 0 40px;
    }

    .property-card {
      background: #161b22;
      padding: 20px;
      width: 300px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.2);
      text-align: center;
      transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

    .property-card:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05);
      box-shadow: 0px 6px 12px rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.3);
    }

    .property-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 180px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0px 2px 6px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    }

    .property-card h2,
    .property-card p {
      color: #e6edf3;
    }

    .view-details {
      margin-top: 15px;
    }

    .view-details a {
      display: inline-block;
      text-decoration: none;
      background-color: #58a6ff;
      color: white;
      padding: 10px 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .view-details a:hover {
      background-color: #1f6feb;
    }

    /* Popular Cities Section */
    .popular-cities {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 80px;
    }

    .city-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding: 0 40px;
    }

    .city-card {
      width: 220px;
      background-color: #161b22;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.15);
    }

    .city-card img {
      width: 100%;
      height: 150px;
      object-fit: cover;
      border-radius: 8px;
    }

    .city-card h3 {
      color: #e6edf3;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }


  
  .accordion-button:focus,
  .accordion-button:hover {
    box-shadow: none !important;
    background-color: #121212 !important; /* ya same bg-dark */
    color: #fff !important;
  }

  .accordion-button:not(.collapsed) {
    background-color: #121212 !important;
    color: #fff !important;
  }



  .accordion-item {
  background: rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.1); /* Blue translucent background */
  border: 1px solid rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.2);
  color: #e6edf3;
  border-radius: 12px;
  margin-bottom: 12px;
  overflow: hidden;
  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
  box-shadow: 0px 4px 10px rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.1);
}

.accordion-button {
  background-color: rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.15);
  color: #58a6ff;
  font-weight: bold;
  box-shadow: none;
  border: none;
  transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
}

.accordion-button:hover,
.accordion-button:focus {
  background-color: rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.25) !important;
  color: #ffffff !important;
  box-shadow: 0px 0px 10px rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.3);
}

.accordion-button:not(.collapsed) {
  background-color: rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.3) !important;
  color: #ffffff !important;
}

.accordion-body {
  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  color: #c9d1d9;
  padding: 20px;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.1);
  border-radius: 0 0 12px 12px;
}



.accordion-button {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1f6feb, #4a90e2); /* Blue gradient */
  color: #ffffff;
  font-weight: bold;
  transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
  border-radius: 0 !important; /* optional: remove round corners if any */
}

.accordion-button:not(.collapsed) {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a4cb3, #2563eb); /* Darker blue when expanded */
  color: #ffffff;
}

.accordion-button:hover,
.accordion-button:focus {
  background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1741a3, #1f5bdd);
  color: #ffffff;
  box-shadow: none;
}


    

    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      color: #999;
      background-color: #0d1117;
      border-top: 1px solid #1c1c1c;
    }

    

  </style>
</head>

<body>

  <div class="page-wrapper">

    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="header">
      <div class="title">CU Enterprises üè∞</div>
      <div class="auth-buttons">
        <a href="/login" class="button">Login</a>
        <a href="/register" class="button">Register</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <div class="main-content" style="margin-top: 5%;">
      <h1>Welcome to Real Estate Platform</h1>

      <h2 style="margin-top: 10%;">Featured Properties</h2>
      <div class="property-list">
        <% properties.forEach(function(property) { %>
          <div class="property-card">
            <img src="<%= property.image %>" alt="<%= property.title %>">
            <h2><%= property.title %></h2>
            <p><strong>Location:</strong> <%= property.location %></p>
            <p><strong>Price:</strong> $<%= property.price %></p>
            <p><strong>Size:</strong> <%= property.size %> sqft</p>
            <div class="view-details">
              <a href="<%= property.link %>" target="_blank">View Details</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        <% }); %>
      </div>

      <!-- Popular Cities -->
      <section class="popular-cities">
        <h2>Popular Cities</h2>
        <div class="city-grid">
          <div class="city-card">
            <img src="/images/mumbai.jpg" alt="Mumbai">
            <h3>Mumbai</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="city-card">
            <img src="/images/delhi.jpg" alt="Delhi">
            <h3>Delhi</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="city-card">
            <img src="/images/banglore.jpg" alt="Bangalore">
            <h3>Bangalore</h3>
          </div>
          <div class="city-card">
            <img src="/images/jaipur.jpg" alt="Jaipur">
            <h3>Jaipur</h3>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>




    <br> <br> <br> <br>

    <div id="carouselExample" class="carousel slide" data-bs-ride="carousel">
        <div class="carousel-inner">
          <div class="carousel-item active">
            <img src="/images/carousel1.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Slide 1" height="600px">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <h5>Find Your Dream Home</h5>
              <p>Luxury listings in top locations.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/carousel2.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Slide 2" height="600px">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <h5>Best Investment Properties</h5>
              <p>Grow your wealth with real estate.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="carousel-item">
            <img src="/images/carousel3.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Slide 3" height="600px">
            <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block">
              <h5>Live Where You Love</h5>
              <p>Explore apartments, villas, and more.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide="prev">
          <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
        </button>
        <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#carouselExample" data-bs-slide="next">
          <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
        </button>
      </div>




      <br> <br> <br>
      <br> <br> <br>
        <!-- FAQ Section starts -->
        <div class="container my-5">
            <h2 class="text-center text-primary mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
            <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="faqAccordion">
              <div class="accordion-item bg-dark text-light border border-secondary">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-dark text-light" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqOne" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqOne">
                    How can I list my property?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="faqOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    You can list your property by creating an account, navigating to the "Add Property" section, and filling in the required details like location, price, photos, and description.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
          
              <div class="accordion-item bg-dark text-light border border-secondary">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-dark text-light" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqTwo">
                    What is the commission rate?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="faqTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    Our platform charges a standard 2% commission on the final sale value. This fee is only applicable upon successful closure of the deal.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
          
              <div class="accordion-item bg-dark text-light border border-secondary">
                <h2 class="accordion-header">
                  <button class="accordion-button collapsed bg-dark text-light" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#faqThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faqThree">
                    How long does it take to sell?
                  </button>
                </h2>
                <div id="faqThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" data-bs-parent="#faqAccordion">
                  <div class="accordion-body">
                    It depends on the location and pricing. Typically, listings in popular areas sell within 2 to 4 weeks. You can boost visibility using featured listing options.
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          



          <br> <br> <br> <br>
    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer class="bg-dark text-light pt-5 pb-4">
        <div class="container text-center text-md-left">
          <div class="row text-center text-md-left">
            <!-- Company Info -->
            <div class="col-md-3 col-lg-3 col-xl-3 mx-auto mt-3">
              <h5 class="text-uppercase mb-4 font-weight-bold text-info">CU Enterprises</h5>
              <p>
                Revolutionizing real estate with transparency and tech. Helping you find your dream property with ease.
              </p>
            </div>
      
            <!-- Links -->
